{"id":"5145","user":{"id":"102024","nickname":"tc","avatar_url":"https://static.codemao.cn/FkFGmkSmcMZQ8CmNmAEjrtwJBQoC","subject_id":0,"work_shop_name":"","work_shop_level":0,"wuhan_medal":false,"has_signed":false},"title":"【好玩的算法】熔岩龙问题","content":"<p><img src=\"https://static.codemao.cn/FtbecLG3xBIvtIYJqWeVcBCmiTRR\"><br></p>\n<p>在代码岛的一片平原上，有一个 32 x 32 的矿场<br></p>\n<p>这个矿场的其中某一个位置上的土有毒。</p>\n<p>源码精灵熔岩龙喜欢吃土，</p>\n<p>而且每只熔岩龙只会吃一点点，所以可以认为矿场里的每一块土都是不会被吃完的。</p>\n<p>但是如果它吃到有毒的土就会在3个小时以后拉肚子。</p>\n<p>现在我们需要在3个小时内找到这块有毒的土，</p>\n<p>我们最少需要多少只熔岩龙？</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>欢迎大家的各种想法。</p>\n<p><br></p>","board_id":"5","board_name":"你问我答","updated_at":1504086747,"created_at":1501100084,"n_views":192,"n_replies":22,"n_comments":0,"is_authorized":false,"is_featured":false,"is_hotted":false,"is_pinned":false,"tutorial_flag":0,"ask_help_flag":0}